PSA: @target has these super soft, loose fitting tanks in a rainbow of colors for $8 right now 🙌🏻 you'll find them by the clothes, not in the workout section. They have a really cute cut with a seam down the back. The fit is really nice and just slightly loose and the fabric is dreamy. They definitely run big so grab a size down from your usual. ⏩Tip: if you plan to sweat big time, go for super light or super dark- those in between colors are a no-no. But for light activity, grab the rainbow because these are cute, comfy, and 8 bucks 🙌🏻🌈

If you still don’t have a 🎯Target RED Debit Card, now is the time! (Make sure you snag the Debit Card—not the Credit Card Version.) Did you know there were two versions?? Now through May 20th, if you sign up for a Target RED Debit Card, you will get a coupon for an extra 10% off your entire purchase—on top of the extra 5% off you get on ANY purchase from Target with the RedCard! (✨Link in profile✨)They’ve never done anything like this before!
.
🌟If you already have a RedCard (debit or cc version), will you comment and let the rest of our group know why you love it?? And how much money it saves you??💰
.
For me, we use our 5% Target Red Debit Card to purchase Disney Gift Cards and get 5% off on all of them to use at Disneyland! You get an extra 5% off on all Black Friday deals, EVERY purchase you make online or in-store, and your online order always ships free with no minimum purchase. It seriously rocks!
.
The Debit Card just links to your checking account. So the money is pulled out of it just like your typical Debit Card. But it saves Target on CC processing fees. So they give you a discount for using their card- hence the 5% off! (Your credit IS NOT pulled with the Debit Card. That is why I push that over the Credit Card version.)
.
✨Link to grab this promo is in my profile or TheMeleaShow.com/TargetREDCard So head over and get signed up! It will save you hundreds of dollars at Target every year!💵 #Target #TargetStyle #deal
